So focus on building on the attraction, making it rise like the waves, higher and higher, to burn like blue stars in the sky.

Focus on what you have and like a woman stirring her love potion, heat it up, turn on the heat and make it burn hotter than lava, brighter than any star, and intensify it to make him feel the fire even more to connect it all with you.

He’s with you because…..you make him feel alive.
